dct_title_s: Formosa photo maps 1:25,000. Takao NW, sheet 2114-I NW. A.M.S. L092
dct_description_sm: AMS 1. Alternate title: Takao, NW, Formosa. Polyconic projection. Name designation changed to Kao-hsuing [Kaohsuing]. Mosaic controlled by average fit to 1:25,000 map. Aerial photographs flown by U.S.A.A.F., Jan, 1944. "Photomap to accompany lesson--[information obliterated]. Subcourse 20-3, common subcourse, map and aerial photograph reading II 203-9-7.".
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1944.
